
This directory contains macros that run over Run 15 IFF trees. 

Code works for 2015 production library: SL16d
compile the code with the command:

starver SL16d
cons

Macro description:

1. StRoot contains main macros (*.cc and *h)
2. Analysis.C is the macro that calls macro within StRoot. 
   This can be  used for interactive running as well with the command: 
	root4star Analysis.C
3. Analysis.xml is the script to submit jobs for the all 2015 runs. Each run has a single root tree and jobs will be submitted for each run and so the output file will produced for each run.


To submit job for full sample simply run the command: 

	star-submit Analysis.xml  

